               </p>
               <p>Mathias Schulze, Waterloo Centre for German Studies, University of Waterloo, 200 University Avenue West, Waterloo, ON, N2L 3G1, Canada, mailto:<email xlink:href="mschulze@uwaterloo.ca">mschulze@uwaterloo.ca</email>, <uri xlink:href="http://www.wcgs.ca/~mschulze">http://wcgs.ca/~mschulze</uri>
